full_summary:
**RFP Title**
Propane Engine Driven Forklift Truck (Groupe 1A-Configuration E)

**Notice Type**
Request for Proposal (RFP) against Supply Arrangement (RFSA) E60HS-21FRKL/A

**Reference**
cb-5568-90426534

**Status**
Expired

**Category**
Goods and Services

**Description of the Requirement**

Public Works and Government Services Canada (PWGSC) requires:

*   Propane Engine Driven Forklift Truck (Groupe 1A - Configuration E)
*   Ancillary items
*   Integrated Logistic Support items

**Key Delivery Requirements**

The requested delivery date for the above-mentioned requirement is within 4-6 weeks from the effective date of the contract.

**Target Supplier Group**
This bid solicitation process is open only to suppliers holding a Supply Arrangement (SA) under the Request (RFSA) E60HS-21FRKL/A. Interested suppliers must first be pre-qualified to participate in this bid solicitation.

**Pre-Qualification Process**
To pre-qualify, please refer to the Supply Arrangement (SA) details provided on Canadabuys.canada.ca.

**Notices and Communication**

*   PWGSC may issue additional notices during the solicitation process.
*   Suppliers can request debriefing sessions for unsuccessful bids within 15 working days after bid rejection notice.

**Timeline**

*   Tender Closing Date: 2023-06-06T14:00:00
*   Amendment Date: 2023-06-06

**Important Contact**
Contracting Authority: Isadora Romero

*   Email: [Isadora.Romero@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:Isadora.Romero@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)
*   Phone: (873) 355-4964

**Countries and Regions**
This solicitation invites bids from suppliers of multiple countries subject to Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA) or Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA) trade agreements. The requirements are specified for delivery in Ontario (except NCR) and across Canada.
